<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kisazo Un Gingtute Haw</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kisazo un gingtutehaw a kikhelh man,
 I hinnau hi phat chawmcha a ding mai a hi;
 Khawvel lopi leh a hawihna cheng chengte hi,
 A matiema hung tuoi ngei ding a hiu.

[V2]
 I umnau lei In hi kiphie mahleh,
 Vana In nuom zaw I nei ui;
 Zietak ahin khaw mun det I nei puoh ngal un,
 Khuo hungum ding chu I hawl zawu ahi.

[V3]
 2. Na neih leh lam na vangsakna cheng cheng te hi,
 Kiletsak leh kilekna'n mang khapalh khan la;
 Khawvel ahin bangmah I lutpih ngal puou a,
 Bangmah pawt dawk pih diek lo ding I hiu.

[V4]
 3. Aw liengvai, Lalpa Aw nemin a hun sam hi,
 Pathien in zie khawvel thila gimthei te hi;
 Ginna a hausa ding leh Amah hehpihte,
 Kawma a tiem gam chu chang ngei dingin.

[V5]
 4. Khawvel ahin haksa takin I um zing ui,
 Galdawt hitiu thagau chawlhna mun det lam chuh;
 Lungkhamna leh buoina gam hi I khelhtieng leh,
 Lalpa kawmah I nawpnau kim tan a.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>310</hymn_number>
</song>